Integrate Python and PySpark for big data.

Use cases:

Opening large CSV files (10GB+)
Processing huge datasets
Filtering millions of rows
Aggregations

Architecture:

Qt app calls Python service.

Python service runs PySpark jobs.

Workflow:

User opens large CSV
Qt sends file path to Python engine
PySpark loads data
Returns chunked data

Use:

PySpark
Apache Arrow
IPC communication

Output Python API design.
